\s URUGENDO RW’ABANA B’IMANA
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Urugendo rw’abana b’Imana, biragoye kurumenya vy’ukuri, iyo ndarwibajije ruransiga, ico nzi gusa kandi nizeye n’uko ab’Imana bari muri rwo\bd*\bd .\bd*
\pc \bdit Ntuz’ugire abo wishimira mw’\bdit*\bdit I\bdit*\bdit jambo, ntuze wiyitirire umuntu n’umwe mw’Ishengero, uz’urondere kubona Imana yonyene mw’ijambo ryayo\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit ./.Ivyo navyo bizoguha guhagarara, kand’uzoshikama mu gakiza./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Iyo nzira bagenda bacamwo, nayo nyene iragoye gutahura, kuko n’ubwenge ntibuyitahura, ariko uwuyihishuriwe wese, arayizera kandi akayibandanya.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ntuz’ugire abo wishimira mw’\bdit*\bdit I\bdit*\bdit jambo, ntuze wiyitirire umuntu n’umwe mw’Ishengero, uz’urondere kubona Imana yonyene mw’ijambo ryayo ./.Ivyo navyo bizoguha guhagarara, kand’uzoshikama mu gakiza./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ncuti zanje ni mumbwire namwe, umunyabwenge arazimira, n’ikijuju naco kikayihusha, ivy’iyo nzira Data, biz’Imana nyen’igikorwa.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ntuz’ugire abo wishimira mw’\bdit*\bdit I\bdit*\bdit jambo, ntuze wiyitirire umuntu n’umwe mw’Ishengero, uz’urondere kubona Imana yonyene mw’ijambo ryayo ./.Ivyo navyo bizoguha guhagarara, kand’uzoshikama mu gakiza./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd N’uko bene Data nkunda cane, iyo nzira uzuyibaze Imana gusa, nturabe ivyifuzo vyawe ncuti ariko wiragize Imana yonyene, kuko iri mu guhishurirwa kuzima.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ntuz’ugire abo wishimira mw’\bdit*\bdit I\bdit*\bdit jambo, ntuze wiyitirire umuntu n’umwe mw’Ishengero, uz’urondere kubona Imana yonyene mw’ijambo ryayo ./.Ivyo navyo bizoguha guhagarara, kand’uzoshikama mu gakiza./.\bdit*
